title: Ebro In The Morning - Ebro's In-Flight Drama + Mystikal Arrested + Nicki Minaj Drama
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 8/1/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about January Sixth Arrests, Nicki Minaj's latest drama, and Ebro vs. a flight attendant!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning! 

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
